{"tid":2097025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［雖遠必撤］印度政府消息指在加勒萬河谷的解放軍正後撤","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:01:26.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf000b18089f35d6017428847408304dd7086ccc","tid":2097025,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=396979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396979&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEvxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=4ca32427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396979&h=67df71c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=396979</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】印度政府消息指，中國士兵正從雙方之前爆發衝突的邊境地區撤走。<br />\n<br />\n中印軍隊上月中在有主權爭議的邊境地區加勒萬河谷爆發武力衝突，造成20名印度士兵死亡，解放軍傷亡人數未明。<br />\n<br />\n印度傳媒引述政府消息報道，解放軍在周一拆除加勒萬河谷和戈格拉溫泉的部分帳幕和臨時建築物，軍車就駛離逾一公里，重設緩衝區。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅被問到在加勒萬河谷的解放軍是否後撤時說，中印雙方正採取有效措施緩和邊境局勢，又說中方希望跟印度相向而行，以實際行動落實雙方達成的共識，繼續透過外交及軍事渠道保持密切溝通，共同推動邊境局勢降溫。"},{"pid":"43acc4ce73ced3c01de343798211530dbc834335","tid":2097025,"uid":152387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"點解外交部唔強烈譴責解放軍暴力行為?<br />\n死咗廿個人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4defd801b1b105a903c199c19bd1ae062ba49740","tid":2097025,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"想要幾多地 任你攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n割走埋西藏都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ad494ab6ca6dbf681b5ec7ba73c77f3b7029a","tid":2097025,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedB